---
export const prerender = true;
import BlogLayout from '../../layouts/BlogLayout.astro';
import '../../styles/global.css';
---

<BlogLayout
  title="Beginner Guides — Learn Scrabble From Scratch"
  description="Complete collection of beginner Scrabble guides. Learn the rules, scoring, strategy, and etiquette. Free guides with no signup required."
  keywords="scrabble beginner guide, learn scrabble, scrabble rules, how to play scrabble, scrabble tips for beginners, scrabble scoring, free scrabble guide"
>
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "FAQPage",
    "mainEntity": [
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "What should a beginner learn first in Scrabble?",
        "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Start with the basic rules and board layout, then learn tile values and how scoring works. Once you understand the mechanics, move on to premium squares and simple two-letter words to build your confidence." }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "How long does it take to get good at Scrabble?",
        "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Most players see noticeable improvement within a few weeks of regular play. Learning the two-letter words and basic tile management can boost your score by 50-100 points per game almost immediately." }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Do I need to memorise the entire Scrabble dictionary?",
        "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "No. Knowing just the 127 two-letter words and a handful of high-value short words gives beginners a major advantage. Focus on playable words rather than obscure ones." }
      }
    ]
  })} />

  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <nav class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-6 flex items-center gap-1">
      <a href="/blog/" class="hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">← Blog</a>
      <span class="mx-1">›</span>
      <span class="text-gray-300">Beginner Guides</span>
    </nav>

    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Beginner Guides</h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 mb-6">
      New to Scrabble? Start here. These 10 guides cover everything from the basic rules to winning strategy, 
      scoring mechanics, and table etiquette. Each article is written for players who are just getting started 
      — no jargon, no assumptions, just clear explanations to help you play with confidence.
    </p>

    <!-- Stat Strip: Category Overview -->
    <div class="not-prose my-8 p-4 rounded-xl border border-emerald-500/30 bg-emerald-950/10">
      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-6 text-center">
        <div><p class="text-2xl font-bold text-emerald-400">10</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Guides</p></div>
        <div><p class="text-2xl font-bold text-emerald-400">0</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Jargon</p></div>
        <div><p class="text-2xl font-bold text-emerald-400">Free</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Always</p></div>
        <div><p class="text-2xl font-bold text-emerald-400">5 min</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Avg Read</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Insight Callout -->
    <div class="not-prose my-6 p-5 rounded-xl border border-blue-500/30 bg-blue-950/20">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-blue-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">💡 The Beginner's Edge</p>
      <p class="text-base text-gray-200">You don't need a huge vocabulary to win at Scrabble. Knowing just <span class="text-white font-medium">127 two-letter words</span> and understanding <span class="text-white font-medium">premium square placement</span> gives new players a bigger advantage than memorising thousands of obscure words. Strategy beats vocabulary at every skill level.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Learning Path Pill Badges -->
    <div class="not-prose my-6 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-3">
      <span class="text-xs text-gray-400 mr-2">Learning Path:</span>
      <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-sm">
        <span class="text-white font-bold">1.</span><span class="text-emerald-400 text-xs">Rules</span>
      </span>
      <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-sm">
        <span class="text-white font-bold">2.</span><span class="text-emerald-400 text-xs">Scoring</span>
      </span>
      <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-sm">
        <span class="text-white font-bold">3.</span><span class="text-emerald-400 text-xs">Board</span>
      </span>
      <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-sm">
        <span class="text-white font-bold">4.</span><span class="text-emerald-400 text-xs">Strategy</span>
      </span>
      <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-sm">
        <span class="text-white font-bold">5.</span><span class="text-emerald-400 text-xs">Win</span>
      </span>
    </div>

    <!-- Hero Card: The Basics -->
    <div class="not-prose my-8 p-6 rounded-2xl border-2 border-emerald-500/50 bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-950/30 to-teal-950/20 relative overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute top-3 right-4 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-emerald-500/70">📖 Start Here</div>
      <p class="text-2xl font-black text-white tracking-wider mb-2">LEARN THE FUNDAMENTALS</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-emerald-300 font-semibold mb-3">Rules → Scoring → Board → Your first win</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">Every great Scrabble player started by learning these basics. The guides below take you from "what is this game?" to confidently playing your first competitive game. Follow them in order for the smoothest learning curve, or jump to whichever topic you need most.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Section: Understanding the Game -->
    <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">Understanding the Game</h2>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-4">The foundation — what Scrabble is, how a game flows, and the official rules you need to know.</p>

    <div class="grid gap-4 not-prose">
      <a href="/blog/what-is-scrabble/" class="block p-5 rounded-xl border border-green-500/30 bg-green-950/10 hover:border-green-400 transition-all group">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <span class="shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-green-900/50 border border-green-500/40 flex items-center justify-center text-xs text-green-300 font-bold">1</span>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white group-hover:text-green-400 transition-colors">What Is Scrabble?</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-1">An introduction to the world's most popular word game — what it is, who plays it, and why it endures.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>
      <a href="/blog/how-to-play-scrabble/" class="block p-5 rounded-xl border border-green-500/30 bg-green-950/10 hover:border-green-400 transition-all group">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
