          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white group-hover:text-green-400 transition-colors">How to Play Scrabble</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-1">Step-by-step walkthrough of your first game — setup, turns, tile draws, and how to finish.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>
      <a href="/blog/scrabble-rules-explained/" class="block p-5 rounded-xl border border-green-500/30 bg-green-950/10 hover:border-green-400 transition-all group">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
