    <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">Scoring & Board Mastery</h2>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-4">Understand how points work and how to use the board's built-in multipliers to your advantage.</p>

    <!-- Comparison Cards: Scoring -->
    <div class="not-prose my-6 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
      <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-green-500/30 bg-green-950/10">
        <p class="text-green-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">✓ Smart Scoring</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Place high-value tiles (Q, Z, X, J) on premium squares. A Z on a Triple Letter scores 30 points from one tile.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-red-500/30 bg-red-950/10">
        <p class="text-red-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">✗ Common Mistake</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Playing your longest word regardless of position. A short word on a Triple Word square often outscores a long word in the middle.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid gap-4 not-prose">
      <a href="/blog/scrabble-scoring-guide/" class="block p-5 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-950/10 hover:border-amber-400 transition-all group">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <span class="shrink-0 text-amber-400 text-lg">📊</span>
          <div>
